_output:
Respond with JSON only:
{
  "narrative": "1-3 sentences. May contain <WES purpose=\"...\">body</WES> and <AffinityShift>...</AffinityShift> inline.",
  "threads": [
    {
      "headline": "5-8 evocative words",
      "content_tags": ["<3-6 tags from defined categories>"],
      "relationship": "open|continue|reframe|close",
      "parent_thread_id": "NL2 thread_id from below or null",
      "arc_hint": "optional free string"
    }
  ],
  "tags": ["<3-6 tags describing the whole narrative>"]
}

parent_thread_id: set to the strongest NL2 thread_id when promoting a cross-locality pattern; null if the district thread is top-down (driven by region) or a reframe.
Fragment count: 0-3. Skip when nothing has truly crossed locality lines this firing.
